items.title: Awesome Tdengine
items.content_text:
### IoT

*   [IoTSharp (⭐1.2k)](https://github.com/IoTSharp/IoTSharp/blob/master/IoTSharp.Data.TimeSeries/TaosStorage.cs) - IoTSharp is an open-source IoT platform for data collection,It supports storing time series data to TDengine.

### Connector

*   [DBUtility.TDengine (⭐2)](https://github.com/cockroach888/GSA.MOLLE.ToolKits/tree/main/src/ToolKits.DBUtility) - C# Connector for TDengine. (.NET 6+).
*   [IoTSharp.Data.Taos](https://www.nuget.org/packages/IoTSharp.Data.Taos/)  - TDengine's ADO.Net provider. (.Net Framework 4.6+, .Net Standard2.0+,.Net 5.0+).

### Others

*   [IoTSharp.HealthChecks.Taos](https://www.nuget.org/packages/IoTSharp.HealthChecks.Taos/) - TDengine's HealthChecks provider. (.Net 5.0+).
